README(English):

stumpwm-tray is a tray application for stumpwm.I have forked the orignal code from https://github.com/lucashpandolfo,
give my thanks to him:)

However,the forked code could not work properly,so I made some hack in order to make it usable.Now it can work with
tray icon(like rhytmbox、stardict etc.) correctly.

But there is still some problems I need to fix:
1. When run rhytmbox from command line(not by stumpwm's run-shell-command),the tray icon cannot be added to the 
   tray window,and sometimes clx will complaint for wrong type(I donnot know whether this is clx's issue).

====================================================================

README(Simplified Chinese):
stumpwm-tray是一款面向stumpwm的tray应用。我从https://github.com/lucashpandolfo 克隆了原代码，谢谢他。

然而，克隆下来的代码并不能正常工作，因此我进行了些修改使其可用。它现在可以和一些支持tray icon的应用一起正常工作（如rhythmbox、stardict等）。

但是，目前仍一些问题有待解决：
1、当从命令行，而不是使用stumpwm提供的run-shell-command命令中启动rhythmbox时，tray icon不能被正确添加，并且有时clx会报window error
   这个错误（不知道是否是clx的问题）。